text: -[ Sighs ]
Morning, Dwight.
-Who are you?

-[ Scoffs ]
Who am I? I'm Jim.

We've been working together
for 12 years.
Weird joke, Dwight.

-You're not Jim.
Jim's not Asian.
-You seriously never noticed?

Hey. Hats off to you
for not seeing race.

-All right, then, Jim.
Uh, why don't you tell me

about that sale
that you made yesterday?
-Uh, Wellington Systems?

Sold them 10 cases
of 24-pound letter stock.

Or were you talking about
Krieger-Murphy?

Because I didn't
close that one yet,

but I'm hoping I've got
a voicemail from Paul Krieger
waiting for me.
-Please enter your password.
You have one new message.
-How did you know? No! No, no.
That is sensitive information.

Only for employees,
not outsiders!

-Dwight, cut it out.
I'm trying to work.

-You don't work here!
You're not Jim!

-Jim, I got us that dinner
reservation -- Grico's, 7:30.
-Oh, great. Can't wait.

Jim's at the dentist
this morning,

and Steve is
an actor friend of ours.

-I don't know who you are,
but you are not Jim.
This is Jim!
Oh, my --
Oh, d-- Oh, how did -- Hunh!
